  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an observation study of women with gestational diabetes. Subjects recruited undergo
      immediate postpartum diabetic screening prior to discharge. Post-partum screening for overt
      diabetes is repeated 6-12 weeks postpartum. The outcome of interest is the utility of an
      immediate post partum screen for overt diabetes compared to a traditional 6 week test.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
